### 2. âš ï¸ Important: Data Directory Setup
The script requires a specific folder structure to run. Before running the script, you must:

1. Create a folder named "data" in the same directory as the script.
2. Place your CSV files inside this folder.
3. Ensure your CSV filenames start with the building name (e.g., Science_usage.csv, Library_data.csv).

